-- Repsol to base compensation claim on $18 billion YPF value
-- 
-- Tue Apr 17, 2012 5:46am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/17/us-repsol-compensation-idUSBRE83G0FU20120417

 

 MADRID  (Reuters) - The chairman of Repsol ( REP.MC ) said the company would base compensation claims against Argentina for its takeover of its YPF ( YPFD.BA ) unit on a minimum value of the YPF of $18 billion. 
 (Reporting By Tracy Rucinski, writing by Sarah Morris)